OL,5, More students will be able to access   
OL,6, loans in an overhaul to England's      
OL,7, student finance system - but remote    
OL,8, learners will not get maintenance help.
OL,10,FThe government has confirmed plans to  
OL,11,Fallow people to access loans worth the 
OL,12,Fequivalent of four years of post-18    
OL,13,Feducation (#37,000 in today's tuition  
OL,14,Ffees) throughout their lives.          
OL,16,FIt says the lifelong loan entitlement  
OL,17,F(LLE) will make courses more flexible. 
OL,19,FBut maintenance loans will be available
OL,20,Fonly for in-person courses.            
